{
  "texts": [
    "These methods employ various sources for verification, which can be performed manually, semi-automatically and automatically.",
    "Manual methods rely on experts from various fields of expertise to verify claims.",
    "In semi-automatic methods, the wisdom of crowd is utilized to detect disinformation.",
    "In these methods, individuals can annotate content.",
    "Then, by aggregating and analyzing these annotations, an overall assessment of the content veracity is generated."
  ]
}